Rating: 3
Don't waste the stems of the broccoli! Simply cut them away from the broccoli heads, peel then and slice them about 1/4" think and saute with the garlic and lemon zest. I used whole garlic cloves instead of chopped garlic and it made a prettier presentation with the added benefit a sweet flavor from the sauteed garlic. Probably not a good idea for fids though. I too used a shake of red chile peppers. My husbands like the heat!

